And so maybe keeping Newton and keeping Aristotle is not that different from keeping Leonardo.

01:01:06.480 --> 01:01:07.960
You don't teach artists.

01:01:07.960 --> 01:01:11.960
I mean artists have to learn about Leonardo, but you don't teach a professional artist

01:01:11.960 --> 01:01:12.960
now.

01:01:12.960 --> 01:01:14.560
Go out and make art exactly like Leonardo.

01:01:14.560 --> 01:01:20.120
Any more than we teach, go out and do Aristotle's cosmology.

