And so this notion of having projects that everyone can do and you were kind of crowd

01:02:09.000 --> 01:02:11.320
sourcing and all that, you were kind of feeling it.

01:02:11.320 --> 01:02:14.880
There's a really good model in science now for citizen science where there are these

01:02:14.880 --> 01:02:19.840
projects where it's not just because it's cool as an outreach thing to involve people.

