In fact, the science is better.

01:02:21.360 --> 01:02:26.080
There are certain kinds of science where having lots of people out there recording and sensing

01:02:26.080 --> 01:02:31.280
and contributing gives us an ability to do kinds of science that we couldn't do when

01:02:31.280 --> 01:02:32.920
it's just the genius.

01:02:32.920 --> 01:02:37.280
And so the idea, and you mentioned a project at a museum that maybe kind of hinted at

01:02:37.280 --> 01:02:43.120
this too, but the idea of sort of citizen side art where we use some of these same platforms

01:02:43.120 --> 01:02:49.400
to really be collaborative in some way that it's not about the genius vision of the great

01:02:49.400 --> 01:02:53.600
ego, but the contribution of the masses.

